Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *


IMAPAccount posteo
Host posteo.de
User mattiasgiese@posteo.net
PassCmd "pass show internet/dienstleister/posteo"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore posteo-remote
Account posteo

MaildirStore posteo-local
Path ~/mail/posteo/
Inbox ~/mail/posteo/INBOX

Channel posteo-inbox
Master :posteo-remote:
Slave :posteo-local:
Patterns "INBOX"

Channel posteo-sent
Master :posteo-remote:"Sent"
Slave :posteo-local:sent

Channel posteo-trash
Master :posteo-remote:"Trash"
Slave :posteo-local:trash

Group posteo
Channel posteo-inbox
Channel posteo-sent
Channel posteo-trash

IMAPAccount b1
Host imap.intern.b1-systems.de
User giese
PassCmd "pass show b1/general"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore b1-remote
Account b1

MaildirStore b1-local
